@*DK gaxeph
#if defined(INTER)
      SUBROUTINE GTRIG
C ----------------------------------------------------------------------
C. -  B. BLOCH - 850910
C
C  Event   tracking   control routine to replace Geant default
C   Calls   ASPEVE ,ASCEVE from this .HLB
